'''Fortunato''' is the owner of [[Wine Shop]] in [[Draynor Village]]. [[Free players]] can purchase [[jug]]s and [[Jug of wine|jugs of wine]] from him, while [[members]] can additionally purchase [[Bottle of wine|bottles of wine]] and [[Jug of vinegar|jugs of vinegar]] from him once they have started the [[Rag and Bone Man I]] [[quest]]. He will also stop players from stealing from his wine stall if he is near a player attempting to do so (requiring 22 [[Thieving]] and granting 27 [[experience]] per successful attempt).

Fortunato buys back all [[empty wine bottle]]s for 2 [[coins]] a piece. This option, however, does not come up in any dialogue; a player must use the empty wine bottle on him.

If you steal from the wine stall before buying the vinegar from him for the quest, you will have to wait several minutes before you can talk to him without him calling the guards on you.

